    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the rice is cooking, cut a slice of<strong> lemon </strong>per person</p><p>Add your <strong>free range</strong> <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> and a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Top each piece of chicken with a<strong> lemon slice</strong> and put the tray in the oven for 15 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 2,
