      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>shredded kale </strong>to a large baking tray (or two!) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 10-12 min or until crispy – this is your <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>kale</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
