        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and<strong> chopped ginger</strong> with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>lemon stock</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until thickened</p><p>Once thickened, remove from the heat and stir through your <strong>toasted sesame oil </strong>– this is your <strong>lemon & ginger sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
