    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>free range chicken</strong> over the <strong>brown</strong> <strong>rice</strong> with the <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>kale</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>lemon & ginger sauce</strong> and garnish with your<strong> toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
